I"t.<h1 class="no_toc" id="monthly-maintenance-procedures">Monthly Maintenance Procedures</h1>

<p>This page details the steps for maintaining and calibrating EC sensors at our flux sites.  Under normal operating conditions, maintenance trips should occur every 4-6 weeks for each site.  <strong>At least two</strong> lab members are required on each trip.  BB1 &amp; BB2 should always be visited on the same trip.  DSM &amp; RBM can also be visited in one trip to save fuel.</p>

