<h1 id="arrival-procedures">Arrival Procedures</h1>

<ul>
  <li>Text Sara and Rick before leaving the lab, at each site, when leaving site, when return to UBC</li>
  <li>Burns Bog: check in and check out
    <ul>
      <li>Call 604-520-6442 (leave msg if no answer)</li>
    </ul>
  </li>
  <li><strong>In Summer</strong> park away from the grass, spray the car tire with water.</li>
</ul>

