<h1 id="post-trip-procedures">Post Trip Procedures</h1>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">1</strong> Text Sara and Rick when return to UBC</p>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">2</strong> Fill out km’s in log book in car on return to UBC</p>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">3</strong> Upload the files from the USB sticks to vinimet</p>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">4</strong> Copy calibration coefficient files from the laptop</p>
<ul>
  <li>Burns Bog: (“C:\InstrumentCalibrations\LI-7200\SN0816(bb1) or SN0815(bb2)”) to Google Drive (Micromet Lab\Projects\2014-Burns Bog\Flux-tower (1)\Calibrations\LI-7200\SN0816 - for BB1)
    <h3 id="need-dsm--rmb">Need DSM &amp; RMB</h3>
  </li>
</ul>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">5</strong> Upload EC high-frequency data to vinimet</p>
<ul>
  <li>To connect to vinimet, use windows &gt; run &gt; \vinimet.geog.ubc.ca  (worker &gt; ponderosa) and empty USB sticks</li>
</ul>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">6</strong> Charge the laptop</p>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">7</strong> Place desiccant in the oven</p>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">8</strong> Update field site logs</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1phokxNzc-gJkWIO1zGLUFsSeRgjsq0HE8QAfLlrlNyI/edit#gid=0">BB1 &amp; BB2</a> - <em>same sheet different tabs</em></li>
  <li><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/1USa7IDpj0D79C8OfFDEoDFKIwjKt0LdVh5fMt04BgpI/edit#gid=0">DSM</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://docs.google.com/spreadsheets/d/114pSwgLBPEeqIezTTIJ4a4Z3kaJhgRvSJZAls8mEOrI?authuser=thruhikerflash%40gmail.com&amp;usp=drive_fs">RBM</a></li>
</ul>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">9</strong> Upload pictures of gas tank/sensors/landscape to google drive (project/site/photos/yyyymmdd)</p>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">10</strong> Upload wildlife camera to google drive (project/site/photos/wildlife camera/yyyymmdd) and reformat the memory card</p>

<p><strong class="label label-purple">11</strong> Input the manually measured WTD to:</p>
<ul>
  <li><a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/1CxYCqgWcYUiZjOije5Yk_igRCdI4IJgF">BB1</a></li>
  <li><a href="https://drive.google.com/drive/u/0/folders/157GZaM88Lz35QuXfYALlAXnDx9IydBGg">BB2</a></li>
</ul>
